txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Very sharp claws from the turtles and toads west of the Ranger-outpost at Tinnudir. You are to deliver the items to the Ranger Astiul at the outpost on the shores of Lake Evendim.
'We will make use of all that you can deliver to us. Claws can be used as toggles, even weapons if needed -- little work is needed to refit these items.'
Wardens of Ann√∫minas Task: Very Sharp Claws
Tinnudir, a Ranger-outpost on the eastern shore of Lake Evendim, is home to the Rangers of Evendim. There, at the outpost, a Ranger named Astiul awaits the return of very sharp claws.
Deliver the very sharp claws to Astiul at the Ranger-outpost of Tinnudir
You have been tasked with collecting very sharp claws from the turtles and toads west of Tinnudir. You are to deliver the items to the Ranger Astiul within the lakeside outpost.
Wanted: Very sharp claws from the turtles and toads west of the Ranger-outpost at Tinnudir.
